<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>반려동물 커뮤니티</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="fontawesome/css/all.min.css"> <!-- https://fontawesome.com/ -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Source+Sans+Pro&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"> <!-- https://fonts.google.com/ -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.4.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-Vkoo8x4CGsO3+Hhxv8T/Q5PaXtkKtu6ug5TOeNV6gBiFeWPGFN9MuhOf23Q9Ifjh" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/singup.css">

</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="user">
        <div class="user-header">
            <h2>회원 가입을 위해 정보를 입력해주세요</h2>
        </div>
    
        <div class="user-info">
            <form>
                <div class="user-id">
                  <label for="exampleInputId1" class="form-label">아이디</label>
                  <input type="text" class="form-control">
                  <div id="IdHelp" class="form-text">영문 대소문자/숫자 4~16자</div>
                </div>
                <div class="user-pw">
                  <label for="exampleInputPassword1" class="form-label">비밀번호</label>
                  <input type="password" class="form-control">
                  <div id="pwHelp" class="form-text">영문 대소문자/숫자/특수문자 조합 8~16자</div>
                </div>
                <div class="user-pw-check">
                  <label for="exampleInputPasswordcheck1" class="form-label">비밀번호 확인</label>
                  <input type="password" class="form-control">
                  </div>
                <div class="user-nickname">
                  <label for="exampleInputINickname1" class="form-label">닉네임</label>
                  <input type="text" class="form-control">
                  <div id="nicknameHelp" class="form-text">한글/영문/숫자 1~16자</div>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" onclick="alert('정말로 가입하시겠습니까?')">가입하기</button>
            </form>                        
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

    
   




    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
